publisher			Rovio Stars							
publish_time	 2013年12月16日		
desc_long							评测						“If you're a fan of adventure games, this is a no-brainer.”9.5/10 – Destructoid“The Point-And-Click adventure that stole my heart.”5/5 – Touch Arcade“Wonderfully imaginative settings and equally fantastic puzzle solutions”5/5 – Gamezebo												关于这款游戏							In a world of greed, corruption and injustice, one little guy decides to stand up for the little guy! Say hello to Tiny Thief, an unconventional hero who uses cunning and trickery to out-smart his opponents across six epic medieval adventures. But beware! He faces fearsome foes, like the Dark Knight, rogue pirates and even a giant robot! Tiny Thief brings back the magic from the point-and-click games of old, charming you with its very own visual style and offbeat sense of humor. The game throws some seriously mind-boggling puzzles at you, with tons of surprising interactive gameplay elements along the way. So get ready to embark on an epic quest to save a princess and kingdom in peril!Tiny Thief is ready to start his big adventure. Are you?Key FeaturesSix big adventures Sneak and steal your way through six epic quests, featuring an awesome pirate ship and daring castle siege!Use cunning and skillOut-smart your tricky opponents using the element of surprise and some downright sneakiness!Unexpected surprisesExplore fully interactive levels and uncover hidden treasures and other surprises at every turn!						
